<P>__{(anxiously)}
<D>__{frances, you remember my lawyer, alma styles?}
<C>__{styles}
<D>__{hello, frances. you seem to be having quite a time of it.}
<C>__{lillian}
<D>__{i called alma because i think we'll need...}
<C>__{styles}
<D>__{frances, the doctors at meadow wood have petitioned the court for your return. your mother has asked me to intervene so you can stay here.}
<C>__{lillian}
<D>__{i swear i didn't know what they were doing to you. i wouldn't have let them...}
<A>__{she bursts into tears. frances takes her in her arms and rocks her like a child.}
