<D>__{it's okay, mama. it's okay.}
<C>__{styles}
<D>__{you realize, of course, your mother is now your legal guardian. in the eyes of the law, you no longer have any rights as an adult. you're going to have to hold your tongue and be selective about whom you mix with. that man who drove you here, for instance }
